            "content": "# Debugging\n\n## Architecture overview\n\n```\nFrontend (DaemonSessionController.ts)\n    ↓ WebSocket JSON-RPC\nDaemon (droid-request-handler.ts)\n    ↓ stdin/stdout JSON-RPC\nCLI (streamingJsonRpcExecRunner.ts)\n```\n\nSee [systems/daemon-cli-protocol.md](../systems/daemon-cli-protocol.md) for the full protocol description.\n\n## Log locations\n\n| Environment | Directory | Key files |\n|---|---|---|\n| Development | `~/.factory-dev/logs/` | `factoryd.log`, `droid-log-single.log`, `console.log` |\n| Production | `~/.factory/logs/` | Same names |\n\nDev server logs (for `npm run dev:web`):\n\n| App | Log file |\n|---|---|\n| backend | `/tmp/factory-dev-backend.log` |\n| daemon | `/tmp/factory-dev-daemon.log` |\n| admin | `/tmp/factory-dev-admin.log` |\n| desktop | `/tmp/factory-dev-desktop.log` |\n\n```bash\ntail -f ~/.factory-dev/logs/factoryd.log  # live daemon log\ntail -f ~/.factory-dev/logs/droid-log-single.log  # live CLI log\n```\n\n## Tracing messages between layers\n\n```bash\n# 1. Did the CLI emit the message?\ngrep \"your-feature\" ~/.factory-dev/logs/droid-log-single.log\n\n# 2. Did the daemon receive and forward it?\ngrep \"your-feature\" ~/.factory-dev/logs/factoryd.log\n\n# 3. Watch all logs in real time\ntail -f ~/.factory-dev/logs/*.log\n```\n\n## Common issues\n\n### Changes not taking effect\n\nAfter modifying CLI or daemon source:\n1. `cd apps/cli && npm run setup` (rebuilds and links wrappers)\n2. Kill and restart the daemon process\n3. Start a **new session** — existing sessions use the binary that spawned them\n\n### Schema mismatches (frontend not receiving events)\n\nIf the CLI sends a notification that the frontend doesn't show:\n1. Is the type in `SessionNotificationType` enum? (`packages/common/src/droid/enums.ts`)\n2. Is the schema defined? (`packages/common/src/droid/schemas/cli.ts`)\n3. Is there a frontend handler? (`packages/frontend/src/services/session/DaemonSessionController.ts`)\n\n### Timing issues\n\nNotifications sent before the session is registered with the daemon are silently dropped. Emit events only after session initialization completes.\n\n### Dev vs prod confusion\n\nCheck which directory you're tailing — `~/.factory-dev/` (dev) vs `~/.factory/` (prod). Mixing them up is the most common cause of \"I see no logs.\"\n\n## Adding debug logging\n\n```typescript\nimport { logInfo } from '@factory/logging';\n\nlogInfo('[MyFeature] event received', { count: items.length });\n```\n\nNever log secrets. The logging package (`packages/logging/`) automatically scrubs known patterns before writing to disk and Sentry.\n\n## Key files for debugging the communication stack\n\n| Layer | File |\n|---|---|\n| Protocol contracts | `packages/common/src/droid/enums.ts`, `packages/common/src/droid/schemas/` |\n| CLI sender | `apps/cli/src/exec/streamingJsonRpcExecRunner.ts` |\n| Daemon handler | `packages/daemon-core/src/droid/` |\n| Frontend receiver | `packages/frontend/src/services/session/DaemonSessionController.ts` |\n\nFull debugging guide: `docs/debugging-daemon.md`.\n",
