            "content": "# Apps\n\nThe Factory monorepo has 21 apps. The six core apps that every engineer works with are:\n\n| App | Type | Port | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| [cli](./cli/index.md) | Bun CLI | — | Droid CLI — the primary AI agent interface |\n| [daemon](./daemon.md) | Bun service | 37643/41723 | `factoryd` — local broker between CLI and frontends |\n| [backend](./backend.md) | Next.js 15 | 3000 | REST API service |\n| [web](./web.md) | Vite + React | 3002 | Web UI for session viewing |\n| [desktop](./desktop.md) | Electron | — | Desktop app wrapping the web UI |\n| [admin](./admin.md) | Next.js 15 | 3001 | Internal admin dashboard |\n\nSupporting apps:\n\n| App | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/signal` | Analytics pipeline for session event processing |\n| `apps/relay` | Proxy for routing daemon traffic from CDEs |\n| `apps/functions` | Firebase Cloud Functions (webhooks, crons) |\n| `apps/factory-vscode-extension` | VS Code integration |\n| `apps/bridge` | Bridge protocol for workspace connections |\n| `apps/bridge-cli-mcp-server` | MCP server bridge for CLI |\n| `apps/scripts` | Build, deployment, and maintenance scripts |\n| `apps/storybook` | Component library storybook |\n\n## Communication overview\n\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    CLI[\"apps/cli\\n(Droid agent)\"]\n    DAEMON[\"apps/daemon\\n(factoryd)\"]\n    WEB[\"apps/web\"]\n    DESK[\"apps/desktop\"]\n    BACKEND[\"apps/backend\"]\n\n    CLI -->|\"stdout JSON-RPC\"| DAEMON\n    WEB -->|\"WebSocket\"| DAEMON\n    DESK -->|\"WebSocket\"| DAEMON\n    DAEMON -->|\"spawns\"| CLI\n    CLI -->|\"HTTP\"| BACKEND\n    DAEMON -->|\"HTTP\"| BACKEND\n```\n\nAll JSON-RPC schema contracts are in `packages/common/src/droid/`.\n",
