            "content": "# Web (apps/web)\n\nActive contributors: luke, theo, sherry\n\n## Purpose\n\n`apps/web` is the main web interface for the Factory platform — a Vite + React app where users can view and interact with Droid sessions, manage repositories, and browse wikis. It's the primary visual companion to the Droid CLI for users who prefer a browser interface.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\napps/web/src/\n├── main.tsx          # Entry point — React root, auth provider setup\n├── auth/             # WorkOS AuthKit integration\n│   ├── callback.tsx  # OAuth callback handler\n│   └── ...\n├── config/           # App configuration\n└── types/            # Web-specific types\n\napps/web/e2e/         # Playwright E2E tests\n```\n\nThe web app is intentionally thin — most feature logic lives in `packages/frontend/` to share it with `apps/desktop`.\n\n## How it works\n\nThe web app is a Vite SPA. Auth is handled by WorkOS AuthKit (`@workos-inc/authkit-react`). After login, the app connects to the backend API and, for active sessions, opens a WebSocket connection to the daemon (`factoryd`).\n\nThe session UI (`packages/frontend/src/features/sessions/`) is the main view. It renders conversation history, tool results, file diffs, and terminal output.\n\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    Web[\"apps/web (SPA)\"] --> Frontend[\"packages/frontend\\n(session UI, hooks, services)\"]\n    Frontend --> CoreUI[\"@factory/core-ui\\n(design system)\"]\n    Frontend --> DroidCore[\"@factory/droid-core\\n(message types)\"]\n    Frontend --> Common[\"@factory/common\\n(types, enums)\"]\n    Web --> Backend[\"apps/backend\\n(REST API)\"]\n    Frontend --> Daemon[\"apps/daemon\\n(WebSocket)\"]\n```\n\n## E2E testing\n\nPlaywright tests live in `apps/web/e2e/`. Run them:\n\n```bash\ncd apps/web && npm run test:e2e          # headless\ncd apps/web && npm run test:e2e -- --headed --debug  # visual\n```\n\nSee `apps/web/playwright.config.ts` for test configuration.\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/main.tsx` | Entry point |\n| `src/auth/` | WorkOS auth integration |\n| `e2e/` | Playwright E2E tests |\n\nFor the session UI implementation, see [packages/frontend](../packages/frontend.md). For the design system, see [packages/core-ui](../packages/core-ui.md).\n",
