            "content": "# Feature flags\n\n## Purpose\n\nFeature flags let the team ship code behind a gate that can be enabled per-org or globally without redeployment. Factory uses [Statsig](https://statsig.com) as the feature gate provider.\n\n## The flag catalog\n\nAll flag definitions live in `packages/common/src/feature-flags/constants.ts`:\n\n```typescript\nexport const FactoryFeatureFlags = {\n  MyFeature: {\n    displayName: 'My Feature',\n    statsigName: 'my_feature',   // matches the gate name in Statsig console\n    defaultValue: false,\n  },\n};\n```\n\nThis is one of the most frequently changed files in the codebase — 78 changes in the last 90 days.\n\n## Using flags\n\n### React components (frontend)\n\n```typescript\nimport { useFeatureFlagValue } from '@/featureFlags';\nimport { FactoryFeatureFlags } from '@factory/common/feature-flags';\n\nfunction MyComponent() {\n  const isEnabled = useFeatureFlagValue(FactoryFeatureFlags.MyFeature);\n  return isEnabled ? <NewFeature /> : null;\n}\n```\n\n### Backend (server-side)\n\n```typescript\nimport { getFeatureFlagInstance } from '@/features/feature-flags/server';\nimport { FactoryFeatureFlags } from '@factory/common/feature-flags';\n\nconst featureFlags = await getFeatureFlagInstance();\nconst isEnabled = await featureFlags.checkFlag(\n  FactoryFeatureFlags.MyFeature,\n  firestoreOrgId\n);\n```\n\n### CLI\n\nThe CLI fetches flags from the backend at startup and caches them to disk. The cache is invalidated after login.\n\n```typescript\nimport { initAskUserToolFlag } from '@/feature-flags/service';\nawait initAskUserToolFlag();\n```\n\n## Flag lifecycle\n\n1. Create the gate in the [Statsig console](https://console.statsig.com/)\n2. Add the definition to `FactoryFeatureFlags` in `packages/common/src/feature-flags/constants.ts`\n3. Gate the feature in code\n4. Roll out the gate gradually or by org in the Statsig console\n5. When the feature is fully launched, remove the flag check and delete the Statsig gate\n6. Remove the constant from `FactoryFeatureFlags`\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `packages/common/src/feature-flags/constants.ts` | Flag catalog |\n| `apps/backend/src/features/feature-flags/` | Server-side flag evaluation |\n| `packages/frontend/src/features/feature-flags/` | Client-side flag hooks |\n| `apps/cli/src/feature-flags/service.ts` | CLI flag initialization |\n\nFull guide: `docs/feature-flags.md`.\n",
