            "content": "# How to monitor\n\nFactory runs multiple services in production. This section covers how to observe them.\n\n## Services and where they run\n\n| Service | Runtime | Monitoring |\n|---|---|---|\n| `apps/backend` | Vercel | Sentry, custom telemetry |\n| `apps/daemon` (local) | User's machine | Log files |\n| `apps/daemon` (CDE) | E2B sandbox | OTEL tracing, log files |\n| `apps/cli` | User's machine | Log files, Sentry |\n| `apps/admin` | Vercel | Sentry |\n| Firebase/Firestore | Google Cloud | Firebase console |\n\n## Subsections\n\n- [Logging](./logging.md) — where logs go, how to query, log levels\n- [Metrics](./metrics.md) — what's tracked, key metrics\n- [Tracing](./tracing.md) — distributed tracing setup\n- [Alerting](./alerting.md) — alert thresholds, escalation\n",
