            "content": "# Background\n\nContext for architectural decisions, pitfalls, and historical choices that affect how you work with this codebase.\n\n## Subsections\n\n- [Design decisions](./design-decisions.md) — why key architectural choices were made\n- [Pitfalls](./pitfalls.md) — traps and gotchas to watch out for\n\n## When to read this\n\n- Before making changes to the daemon–CLI protocol — the timing constraints are non-obvious\n- Before adding a new LLM provider — understand the adapter pattern\n- Before refactoring the session state — the \"assembly\" naming has history\n",
