            "content": "# Configuration\n\n## Environment variable system\n\nFactory uses `@factory/environment` (`packages/environment/`) for typed environment variable access. Direct `process.env` usage is banned by the `no-direct-process-env` ESLint rule.\n\n```typescript\nimport { getEnvironment } from '@factory/environment';\nconst env = getEnvironment();\n```\n\n## Environment files\n\nEach app has layered env files (lowest to highest precedence):\n\n1. `.env` — committed defaults\n2. `.env.<environment>` — environment-specific (e.g., `.env.development`, `.env.production`)\n3. `.env.local` — local overrides (gitignored)\n\nEnvironments: `development`, `staging`, `preprod`, `production`, `localhost`\n\n## Key environment variables\n\n### CLI (`apps/cli/`)\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `FACTORY_API_URL` | Backend API base URL |\n| `FACTORY_API_KEY` | API key for programmatic/CI use |\n| `FACTORY_ENV` | Environment name (`development`, `production`, etc.) |\n\n### Daemon (`apps/daemon/`)\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `FACTORYD_DISABLE_AUTO_UPDATE` | Set `true` to skip auto-update (used by Electron) |\n| `FACTORY_MACHINE_TYPE` | Machine type (`local`, `ephemeral`, `computer`) |\n| `FACTORY_REMOTE_MACHINE_ID` | Remote machine ID for CDE sessions |\n| `FACTORY_OTEL_ENABLED` | Enable OTEL distributed tracing |\n\n### Backend (`apps/backend/`)\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `WORKOS_API_KEY` | WorkOS API key for auth |\n| `WORKOS_CLIENT_ID` | WorkOS client ID |\n| `STATSIG_SERVER_SECRET_KEY` | Statsig server SDK key |\n| `FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT` | Firebase service account JSON |\n| `ORB_API_KEY` | Orb billing API key |\n\n## Daemon ports\n\n| Environment | Port |\n|---|---|\n| Production | 37643 |\n| Development | 41723 |\n\nDefined in `packages/common/src/daemon/` as `WS_SERVER_CONFIG`.\n\n## Log directories\n\n| Environment | Directory |\n|---|---|\n| Production | `~/.factory/` |\n| Development | `~/.factory-dev/` |\n\n## Turbo cache\n\nCache artifacts stored in `.turbo/` and `**/*/.turbo/`. Clear with `npm run clean:turbo`.\n",
