            "content": "# Data models\n\nCore data structures used throughout the platform. All types are defined in `@factory/common` (`packages/common/src/`).\n\n## Session\n\nA session represents a single Droid work interaction. Types in `packages/common/src/session/`.\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `id` | `string` (UUID) | Unique session identifier |\n| `orgId` | `string` | Organization the session belongs to |\n| `userId` | `string` | User who created the session |\n| `status` | `SessionStatus` | `active`, `completed`, `error`, etc. |\n| `messages` | `Message[]` | Conversation history |\n| `model` | `string` | LLM model used |\n| `createdAt` | `Timestamp` | Creation time |\n\n## Message\n\nA message in a session conversation. Types in `packages/common/src/session/`.\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `id` | `string` | Unique message ID |\n| `role` | `'user' \\| 'assistant'` | Who sent the message |\n| `content` | `Content[]` | Message content blocks |\n| `toolCalls` | `ToolCall[]` | Tool calls made in this message |\n| `createdAt` | `Timestamp` | Message timestamp |\n\n## Organization\n\nAn organization owns sessions, users, and billing. Types in `packages/common/src/organization/`.\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `id` | `string` | Firestore org ID |\n| `workosOrgId` | `string` | WorkOS organization ID |\n| `name` | `string` | Display name |\n| `plan` | `Plan` | Current subscription plan |\n\n## Tool result\n\nResult from a tool call. Types in `packages/common/src/tools/`.\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `toolCallId` | `string` | ID matching the tool call |\n| `type` | `ToolResultType` | Type of result (file, shell, search, etc.) |\n| `content` | `string` | Result content |\n| `isError` | `boolean` | Whether the tool call failed |\n\n## Feature flag\n\nFeature gate definition. Types in `packages/common/src/feature-flags/`.\n\n```typescript\ninterface FeatureFlagDefinition {\n  displayName: string;\n  statsigName: string;\n  defaultValue: boolean;\n}\n```\n\n## SessionNotificationType\n\nAll JSON-RPC notification types the CLI can emit. Full list in `packages/common/src/droid/enums.ts`. Key types:\n\n| Type | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `session.message.created` | New assistant message started |\n| `session.message.chunk` | Streamed token |\n| `session.message.completed` | Message finished |\n| `session.tool.started` | Tool call began |\n| `session.tool.completed` | Tool call finished with result |\n| `session.completed` | Session finished |\n| `session.error` | Session encountered an error |\n",
