            "content": "# Dependencies\n\nKey external dependencies and their versions as of the wiki generation date.\n\n## Runtime\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `bun` | 1.3.10 | Runtime for CLI and daemon |\n| Node.js | 18.x | Runtime for backend, admin, web |\n| `turbo` | ^2.6.3 | Monorepo build orchestrator |\n\n## LLM providers\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `@anthropic-ai/sdk` | (via droid-core) | Anthropic Claude API client |\n| `openai` | ^6.25.0 | OpenAI GPT API client |\n| `@google/genai` | 1.31.0 | Google Gemini API client |\n| AWS SDK | (via Bedrock) | AWS Bedrock for Anthropic via AWS |\n\n## Frontend\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| React | 19 | UI framework |\n| Vite | (apps/web) | Web app bundler |\n| Next.js | 15 | Backend + admin framework |\n| Electron | (apps/desktop) | Desktop app framework |\n| Ink | 6.7.0 | React for terminal (TUI) |\n| Redux Toolkit | ^2.2.7 | State management |\n| styled-components | 6.1.13 | CSS-in-JS styling |\n\n## Auth and identity\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `@workos-inc/node` | ^7.79.3 | WorkOS server SDK |\n| `@workos-inc/authkit-react` | 0.5.1 | WorkOS frontend auth |\n\n## Infrastructure and services\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `firebase-tools` | ^14.4.0 | Firebase CLI |\n| `@statsig/statsig-node-core` | ^0.6.1 | Feature flags |\n| `orb-billing` | ^4.33.0 | Usage billing |\n| `e2b` | ^2.14.0 | Cloud dev environments (CDEs) |\n| `@sentry/nextjs` | ^10.27.0 | Error tracking (backend) |\n| `@sentry/node` | ^10.27.0 | Error tracking (CLI/daemon) |\n| `@slack/web-api` | ^7.9.1 | Slack integration |\n| `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk` | ^1.26.0 | MCP protocol support |\n| `@vscode/ripgrep` | ^1.15.14 | Fast search in CLI tools |\n\n## Build and quality\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `prettier` | ^3.3.3 | Code formatting |\n| `eslint` | (via eslint-config) | Linting |\n| `knip` | ^5.81.0 | Dead code detection |\n| `jest` | ^29.7.0 | Test runner (backend, CLI) |\n| `vitest` | (via frontend) | Test runner (packages/frontend) |\n| `@microsoft/tui-test` | (via cli e2e) | TUI E2E testing |\n| `stylelint` | ^16.10.0 | CSS linting |\n\n## Security overrides\n\nThe root `package.json` has `overrides` for known vulnerable transitive dependencies:\n\n```json\n\"overrides\": {\n  \"cookie@<0.7.0\": \"0.7.0\",\n  \"path-to-regexp@<0.1.10\": \"0.1.10\",\n  \"protobufjs@>=7.0.0 <7.2.5\": \"^7.2.5\"\n}\n```\n",
