            "content": "# @factory/core-ui\n\n**Active contributors (last 90 days):** Ricky S, Andrei Savin, Eno Reyes\n\n## Purpose\n\n`@factory/core-ui` is the mandatory design system for every Factory UI surface. All components in `apps/web`, `apps/desktop`, and `apps/admin` must import from this package rather than using raw HTML elements or creating custom primitives.\n\nCore primitives include: `Box`, `Flex`, `Grid`, `Button`, `IconButton`, `Input`, `TextArea`, `Dropdown`, `Select`, `Modal`, `Toast`, `Tooltip`, `Alert`, `Avatar`, `Card`, `Collapsible`, `ScrollArea`, `Switch`, `Checkbox`, `RadioGroup`, `Tabs`, `Spinner`, `Loading`, `Skeleton`, `Link`, `Video`, `HatchBackground`, `TerminalDropdown`, `ResponsiveSwitch`, and the full `Icon` system (Lucide + custom Factory icons).\n\nTypography: `Header` and `Text` components covering all size/weight variants, plus `TextWithEllipsis` and `TextWithAnimatedEllipsis`.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/core-ui/src/\n├── index.ts                 # Single barrel export for the entire package\n├── primitives/              # 30+ UI components (Box, Button, Input, Modal, …)\n│   ├── Alert/\n│   ├── Avatar/\n│   ├── Box/\n│   ├── Button/\n│   ├── Card/\n│   ├── Checkbox/\n│   ├── Collapsible/\n│   ├── Dropdown/\n│   ├── Flex/\n│   ├── Grid/\n│   ├── HatchBackground/\n│   ├── IconButton/\n│   ├── Input/\n│   ├── Link/\n│   ├── Loading/\n│   ├── Modal/\n│   ├── Radio/\n│   ├── ResponsiveSwitch/\n│   ├── ScrollArea/\n│   ├── Select/\n│   ├── Skeleton/\n│   ├── Spinner/\n│   ├── Switch/\n│   ├── Tabs/\n│   ├── TerminalDropdown/\n│   ├── TextArea/\n│   ├── Toast/\n│   ├── Tooltip/\n│   └── Video/\n├── typography/              # Header, Text, TextWithEllipsis, TextWithAnimatedEllipsis\n├── colors/\n│   ├── constants.ts         # Semantic and palette color values\n│   ├── enums.ts             # ColorMode enum (light / dark)\n│   └── types.ts             # ColorMode, TextColorVariant, SurfaceColorVariant, …\n├── tokens/\n│   ├── constants.ts         # Spacing, radius, shadow design tokens\n│   ├── breakpoints.ts       # Responsive breakpoint values\n│   └── types.ts             # Token types\n├── icons/\n│   ├── Icon.tsx             # Universal <Icon> wrapper\n│   ├── lucide/              # Re-exported Lucide icons\n│   └── custom/              # Factory product icons, MCP server icons, file-type icons\n├── fonts/                   # Font face definitions\n├── hooks/                   # useMountEffect and keyboard shortcut hooks\n├── form/                    # RadioButtonPills (higher-level form component)\n├── styles/                  # Global style helpers\n└── utils/                   # KeyboardShortcut, style-props, platform detection\n```\n\n## Key abstractions\n\n| Abstraction | Location | What it does |\n|-------------|----------|--------------|\n| Layout primitives | `primitives/Box`, `Flex`, `Grid` | Styled-component wrappers that accept CSS-like props (padding, margin, gap, etc.) |\n| Interactive primitives | `primitives/Button`, `Input`, `Select`, `Dropdown`, … | Fully themed form and action controls |\n| Color tokens | `colors/constants.ts` | Semantic palette: `surface`, `text`, `border`, `primary` variants in light and dark |\n| Design tokens | `tokens/constants.ts` | Spacing scale, border radii, shadow levels |\n| Breakpoints | `tokens/breakpoints.ts` | Responsive breakpoints (also exported as `tokens/breakpoints`) |\n| Typography | `typography/Header`, `typography/Text` | Typed heading/body text with variant and color props |\n| Icon system | `icons/Icon.tsx` | Single `<Icon name=\"…\" size=\"…\" color=\"…\" />` component covering Lucide + custom icons |\n| `ResponsiveSwitch` | `primitives/ResponsiveSwitch/` | Renders different subtrees based on `LayoutVariant` (desktop vs. compact) |\n\n## How it works\n\n**Styled-components under the hood.** Every primitive is a styled-component that maps props to CSS. Style props (padding, margin, flex properties) are processed by utility functions in `utils/style-props.ts`.\n\n**Semantic color tokens.** Colors are not hardcoded. Components reference keys from `colors/constants.ts` (e.g., `colors.semantics.surface.default`). The `ColorMode` enum drives light/dark switching at the app level — no component needs to know which mode it's in.\n\n**Storybook for visual testing.** The color palette has dedicated stories in `colors/Colors.stories.tsx`. Each primitive directory typically has its own story file for isolated visual testing.\n\n**`ResponsiveSwitch` + `LayoutVariant`.** The `LayoutVariantProvider` wraps the app tree and tracks whether the UI is in `desktop` or `compact` layout. `useLayoutVariant()` returns the current variant; `ResponsiveSwitch` renders the correct subtree without writing media queries everywhere.\n\n## Integration points\n\nAll three UI apps import from `@factory/core-ui`:\n\n- `apps/web` — main web application\n- `apps/desktop` — Electron desktop shell\n- `apps/admin` — internal admin panel\n\nImport from the package root; all exports go through `src/index.ts`:\n\n```ts\nimport { Box, Flex, Button, Text } from '@factory/core-ui';\nimport { colors } from '@factory/core-ui';\n```\n\nNever import directly from sub-paths like `@factory/core-ui/primitives/Button/Button` — that bypasses the public API.\n\n## Entry points for modification\n\n| What you want to do | Where to start |\n|---------------------|----------------|\n| Add a new primitive component | `packages/core-ui/src/primitives/<ComponentName>/` — create the component, types, enums, and add its export to `src/index.ts` |\n| Add a color token | `packages/core-ui/src/colors/constants.ts` and update `types.ts` if adding a new variant |\n| Add a design token | `packages/core-ui/src/tokens/constants.ts` |\n| Add an icon | Drop into `icons/lucide/` (auto-exported via `icons/lucide/icons.ts`) or `icons/custom/` for product-specific icons |\n| Change typography scale | `packages/core-ui/src/typography/` |\n",
            "file_path": "/Users/jonathanlucuix-andre/Documents/test-repos/factory-mono/droid-wiki/packages/core-ui.md"
