            "content": "# Packages\n\nThe `packages/` directory contains 22 shared libraries that apps import. Most have `@factory/` scope.\n\n## Core packages (Tier 1)\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| [`@factory/droid-core`](droid-core.md) | AI agent core: LLM integrations, tool definitions, streaming |\n| [`@factory/frontend`](frontend.md) | Shared React features across web and desktop |\n| [`@factory/core-ui`](core-ui.md) | Design system and component library (mandatory for all UI) |\n| [`@factory/common`](common.md) | Shared types, enums, API contracts, feature flag constants |\n| [`@factory/services`](services.md) | Business logic and external service integrations |\n| [`@factory/daemon-core`](daemon-core.md) | Daemon server implementation |\n\n## Utility packages (Tier 2)\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| [`@factory/logging`](logging.md) | Logging utilities, error types, metrics |\n| [`@factory/utils`](utils.md) | Shared utility functions (LLM helpers, shell, string) |\n| [`@factory/models`](models.md) | TypeScript type definitions and data schemas |\n| [`@factory/updater`](updater.md) | Auto-update utilities for CLI and daemon |\n| [`@factory/environment`](environment.md) | Strongly-typed environment variable access |\n| [`@factory/runtime`](runtime.md) | Runtime auth and credentials storage |\n| [`@factory/daemon-client`](daemon-client.md) | Client library for daemon WebSocket |\n\n## Development packages (Tier 3)\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `@factory/eslint-config` | Shared ESLint configuration |\n| `@factory/test-utils` | Shared test utilities |\n| `@factory/component-library` | Chat and session UI components |\n| `@factory/mcp` | MCP protocol primitives |\n| `@factory/signal-core` | Signal service primitives |\n| `@factory/droid-sdk` | Droid API SDK for external use |\n\n## Dependency rules\n\n- Apps can import any package\n- Packages can import other packages but must avoid circular dependencies\n- `internal/` packages (`@factory-internal/*`) cannot be imported by public packages\n- All API types must be defined in `@factory/common`\n\n## Key cross-cutting concerns\n\nFeature flags → `@factory/common/src/feature-flags/`  \nError types → `@factory/logging/errors`  \nLLM model registry → `@factory/utils/src/llm/model-registry.ts`  \nSettings → `@factory/services`\n",
