            "content": "# @factory/droid-core\n\nActive contributors: l30t, Leo Tchourakov, Abhay Singhal, Stepan, theo\n\n## Purpose\n\n`@factory/droid-core` is the AI agent core library. It provides LLM provider integrations (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google), tool definitions, message handling, and streaming utilities. Both the CLI and daemon import from this package.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/droid-core/src/\n├── api/               # API client utilities\n├── automations/       # Automation definition types\n├── core/              # Core agent types\n├── droids/            # Custom droid configuration\n├── feature-flags/     # Feature flag hooks for droid-core\n├── llms/\n│   ├── provider/      # LLM provider implementations (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google)\n│   ├── errors/        # LLM-specific error types\n│   ├── types.ts       # LLM request/response types\n│   └── price.ts       # Token pricing data\n├── machine-connection/ # Remote machine connection utilities\n├── messages/          # Message construction and formatting\n├── prompts/           # Prompt building utilities\n├── streaming/         # Streaming response handling\n└── tools/             # Tool definition framework\n    └── utils/         # Tool utility functions (35 files)\n```\n\n## Key abstractions\n\n| File | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `src/llms/provider/` | Provider implementations: Anthropic, OpenAI, Google GenAI |\n| `src/streaming/` | Streaming utilities for LLM token streams |\n| `src/tools/` | Tool schema definitions and execution framework |\n| `src/messages/` | Message construction (system prompt blocks, user messages) |\n| `src/prompts/` | System prompt assembly |\n| `src/droids/` | Custom droid (subagent) configuration types |\n\n## LLM providers\n\nThe package implements provider adapters for:\n- **Anthropic** (Claude models) — primary provider\n- **OpenAI** (GPT models and o-series)\n- **Google GenAI** (Gemini models)\n\nEach provider adapter normalizes the provider's streaming