            "content": "# @factory/daemon-core\n\nActive contributors: factory-sherry, factory-jerry, factory-octavian, factory-daniel\n\n## Purpose\n\n`@factory/daemon-core` contains the main daemon server implementation. The `apps/daemon` entry point is a thin wrapper — all the actual logic lives here. This separation allows the daemon server to be tested independently.\n\n## Key component: droid-request-handler\n\n`src/server/handlers/droid-request-handler.ts` (4,995 lines) implements every RPC method the daemon exposes. This single file handles:\n- Session initialization and lifecycle (~80 RPC methods total)\n- MCP server management\n- Skill listing\n- Automation management\n- Bug report submission\n- File listing and search\n\nIt is the largest source file in the codebase and one of the most critical. Changes here affect every frontend interaction. The corresponding test file (`droid-request-handler.test.ts` at 11,857 lines) is the largest file in the entire repo.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/daemon-core/src/\n├── index.ts           # Exports DaemonCore\n├── types.ts           # Core types\n├── constants.ts       # Daemon constants\n├── server/\n│   └── handlers/\n│       └── droid-request-handler.ts  # All RPC method implementations\n├── droid/             # CLI process spawning and lifecycle management\n├── terminal/          # PTY terminal session management\n├── automations/       # Automation engine\n├── relay/             # Relay client integration\n├── services/          # File, search, and settings services\n└── utils/             # Utilities\n```\n\n## Integration points\n\n- **apps/daemon:** Imports `DaemonCore` as its main server\n- **common:** All RPC method names and schemas from `@factory/common/src/daemon/`\n- **CLI:** Spawns CLI subprocesses via `src/droid/`\n- **Relay:** Connects to relay service via `src/relay/`\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/index.ts` | DaemonCore export |\n| `src/server/handlers/droid-request-handler.ts` | All RPC method implementations |\n| `src/droid/` | CLI subprocess management |\n| `src/terminal/` | PTY terminal sessions |\n| `src/automations/` | Automation scheduling |\n",
