            "content": "# Data models\n\n## Session\n\nDefined in `packages/common/src/session/` and `packages/common/src/sessionV2/`.\n\nKey fields:\n- `id` — UUID v4 session identifier\n- `title` — human-readable name\n- `model` — LLM model used (e.g., `claude-3-5-sonnet`)\n- `messages` — array of `FactoryDroidMessage`\n- `status` — active, closed, archived\n- `createdAt` / `updatedAt` — ISO timestamps\n- `projectDirectory` — filesystem path the session is scoped to\n\n## Message (FactoryDroidMessage)\n\nDefined in `packages/common/src/sessionV2/types.ts`.\n\nKey fields:\n- `id` — unique message ID\n- `role` — `user`, `assistant`, or `tool`\n- `content` — array of `ContentBlock` (text, code, tool_use, tool_result)\n- `visibility` — `visible`, `hidden`, or `debug`\n- `createdAt` — timestamp\n\n## Settings\n\nDefined in `packages/common/src/settings/types.ts`. Large schema with frequently added fields (20 changes in 90 days).\n\nKey areas:\n- Model preferences (default model, reasoning effort)\n- Autonomy level (how much the agent auto-approves)\n- MCP server configurations\n- Custom droid definitions\n- Notification preferences\n\n## Automation\n\nDefined in `packages/common/src/automations/`.\n\nKey fields:\n- `id` — automation ID\n- `name` — human-readable name\n- `trigger` — cron expression or event type\n- `task` — natural language task description\n- `model` — LLM model to use\n- `status` — active, paused\n\n## Feature flag\n\nDefined in `packages/common/src/feature-flags/constants.ts`.\n\n```typescript\ntype FeatureFlag = {\n  displayName: string;\n  statsigName: string; // matches Statsig console\n  defaultValue: boolean;\n};\n```\n\n## Organization\n\nDefined in `packages/common/src/organization/`. Represents the organization context for multi-user scenarios.\n",
