            "content": "# Factory monorepo\n\n> **Summary:** Factory is an AI software engineering platform. The monorepo hosts the `droid` CLI, the `factoryd` background daemon, the web and desktop apps, the backend API, and the shared packages that wire them together. This page gives you the 30-second orientation; every linked page goes deeper.\n\n_Last verified: 2026-03-04 against commit `1cfbf04239`. Confidence: high._\n\n## Table of contents\n\n- [What this repository is](#what-this-repository-is)\n- [Application map](#application-map)\n- [Package map](#package-map)\n- [Quick navigation](#quick-navigation)\n- [Related pages](#related-pages)\n\n## What this repository is\n\nFact: The root `package.json` declares this as an npm workspaces + Turborepo monorepo with `\"workspaces\": [\"apps/*\", \"packages/*\"]` (`package.json` line 7). It uses Bun 1.3.10 and Node 18.x.\n\nThe platform lets users issue instructions to an AI agent (Droid) that runs code, edits files, and interacts with external services inside a sandboxed environment. The three main delivery surfaces are:\n\n1. **Terminal** — the `droid` CLI (interactive TUI or `exec` mode)\n2. **Browser** — `apps/web`, a Vite + React single-page app\n3. **Desktop** — `apps/desktop`, an Electron wrapper around the web app\n\nFact: All three surfaces communicate with the `factoryd` daemon (`apps/daemon`) over WebSocket JSON-RPC 2.0 (`docs/debugging-daemon.md`).\n\n## Application map\n\n| App | Purpose | Port | Stack |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `apps/backend` | REST API, LLM proxy, cron jobs | 3000 | Next.js 15, TypeScript |\n| `apps/admin` | Internal admin dashboard | 3001 | Next.js 15, Redux Toolkit |\n| `apps/web` | Main web chat interface | 3002 | Vite + React 19 |\n| `apps/desktop` | Native desktop app | — | Electron + Vite |\n| `apps/daemon` | Background daemon (`factoryd`) | 37643 prod / 41723 dev | Bun, TypeScript |\n| `apps/cli` | `droid` command-line tool | — | Bun, TypeScript, Ink/React |\n| `apps/factory-vscode-extension` | VS Code integration | — | TypeScript |\n| `apps/functions` | Firebase Cloud Functions | — | Node, TypeScript |\n| `apps/scripts` | Build and maintenance scripts | — | Node, TypeScript |\n\n## Package map\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `@factory/core-ui` | Design system — Box, Button, Input, etc. (mandatory for all UI) |\n| `@factory/common` | Shared enums, constants, API type definitions |\n| `@factory/frontend` | Shared React features, hooks, session service |\n| `@factory/droid-core` | AI agent: tools, LLM providers, message handling, streaming |\n| `@factory/daemon-core` | WebSocket server, terminal manager, droid registry |\n| `@factory/services` | Business logic and external service integrations |\n| `@factory/models` | TypeScript data models and schemas |\n| `@factory/logging` | Centralized logging + error classes |\n| `@factory/utils` | Utility functions |\n| `@factory/updater` | Auto-update logic for CLI and daemon |\n| `@factory/environment` | Strongly-typed environment variable access |\n| `@factory/runtime` | Auth token storage and credential management |\n\n## Quick navigation\n\n- [Architecture and data flows](architecture.md)\n- [Getting started: build, run, test](getting-started.md)\n- [Domains overview](domains/index.md)\n  - [Droid CLI](domains/cli.md)\n  - [Daemon (factoryd)](domains/daemon.md)\n  - [AI agent core](domains/ai-agent.md)\n  - [Web frontend](domains/web-frontend.md)\n  - [Backend API](domains/backend-api.md)\n- [API overview](api/index.md)\n  - [REST endpoints](api/rest-endpoints.md)\n  - [WebSocket JSON-RPC protocol](api/websocket-protocol.md)\n- [Reference](reference/index.md)\n  - [Configuration](reference/configuration.md)\n  - [Data models](reference/data-models.md)\n  - [Package catalog](reference/packages.md)\n\n## Related pages\n\n- [Architecture](architecture.md)\n- [Getting started](getting-started.md)\n- [Domains overview](domains/index.md)\n",
