            "content": "# Release process\n\nFactory uses a continuous release model where `dev` is always deployable and releases are cut periodically.\n\n## Version scheme\n\nVersions follow semver: `0.1.1-dev.N` for dev builds and `0.1.1` for production releases. The current version is in the root `package.json`.\n\n## Normal release flow\n\n1. **Version bump**: `release-bump-version.yml` increments the version across all packages that need it. This creates a commit and a tag.\n2. **Release cut**: `release-cut.yml` runs the full build and deploys all services to production.\n3. **Post-validation**: `post-release-validation.yml` runs smoke tests against production.\n4. **Changelog**: `changelog-docs.yml` generates release notes.\n\n## CLI distribution\n\nThe CLI is distributed two ways:\n\n1. **Direct download (S3)** — `cli-release.yml` builds platform-specific SEA binaries (`droid` on Unix, `droid.exe` on Windows) and uploads to S3. The `droid update` command downloads from S3.\n2. **npm** — `cli-release-npm.yml` publishes to npm for users who prefer `npm install -g @factory/cli`.\n\nPlatform targets: macOS ARM64, macOS x64, Linux ARM64, Linux x64, Windows x64.\n\n## Daemon distribution\n\n`factoryd-release.yml` builds daemon binaries and uploads to S3. The daemon auto-update system (`@factory/updater`) downloads the latest binary at startup when a new version is available.\n\n## Desktop distribution\n\n`desktop-release.yml` builds Electron installers for macOS (`.dmg`, `.zip`), Windows (`.exe`), and Linux (`.AppImage`). Installers are uploaded to S3. The Electron auto-updater checks S3 on startup.\n\n## Hotfixes\n\nFor urgent fixes that cannot wait for the next release:\n\n1. Cut a hotfix branch from `main`.\n2. Apply the fix and PR to `main`.\n3. `hotfix-cut.yml` handles cherry-picking the fix to `dev` and cutting a patch release.\n\n## JetBrains plugin\n\n`jetbrains-plugin-release.yml` publishes to the JetBrains Marketplace.\n\n## VS Code extension\n\n`vscode-extension-release.yml` publishes to the VS Code Marketplace.\n",
