            "content": "# Dependencies\n\nMajor external dependencies and why they're used.\n\n## Runtime and build\n\n| Package | Version | Used in | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n| `bun` | 1.3.10 | `apps/cli`, `apps/daemon`, `apps/relay` | Fast TypeScript runtime |\n| `node` | 18.x | All else | JavaScript runtime (see `.nvmrc`) |\n| `turbo` | 2.x | root | Monorepo build orchestration |\n| `next` | 15 | `apps/backend`, `apps/admin` | Backend framework and SSR |\n| `vite` | 5.x | `apps/web`, `apps/desktop` | Frontend bundler |\n| `electron` | latest | `apps/desktop` | Native desktop shell |\n| `esbuild` | - | `apps/cli`, `apps/daemon` | Fast TypeScript bundler |\n\n## UI\n\n| Package | Used in | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `react` | 19 | All web/desktop UIs | UI framework |\n| `ink` | 6.7.0 | `apps/cli` | Terminal UI (React in TTY) |\n| `@reduxjs/toolkit` | - | `packages/frontend` | State management |\n| `styled-components` | 6.x | `packages/frontend`, `apps/admin` | CSS-in-JS styling |\n| `lucide-react` | 0.457.0 | UI packages | Icon library |\n| `recharts` | - | `apps/admin` | Charts |\n| `@microsoft/tui-test` | - | `apps/cli` | Terminal UI testing |\n| `@playwright/test` | - | `packages/frontend`, `apps/web` | E2E browser testing |\n\n## AI and LLM\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `@anthropic-ai/sdk` | Anthropic Claude API client |\n| `openai` | OpenAI API client |\n| `@google/genai` | Google Gemini API client |\n| `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk` | MCP server/client implementation |\n\n## Auth and security\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `@workos-inc/node` | WorkOS server-side auth |\n| `@workos-inc/authkit-react` | WorkOS client-side React integration |\n| `keytar` | OS keychain access (embedded in CLI bundle) |\n\n## Backend services\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `firebase-admin` | Firestore database access |\n| `@statsig/statsig-node-core` | Feature flag evaluation (server-side) |\n| `@sentry/nextjs` | Error tracking (backend) |\n| `@sentry/node` | Error tracking (daemon/CLI) |\n| `orb-billing` | Orb usage-based billing |\n| `@slack/web-api` | Slack API client |\n| `e2b` | E2B sandbox environments |\n| `dotenv` | Environment variable loading |\n\n## Testing\n\n| Package | Used in | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `jest` | backend, CLI, daemon, packages | Unit testing |\n| `vitest` | `packages/frontend` | Vite-native unit testing |\n| `@testing-library/react` | frontend tests | React component testing |\n| `ts-jest` | Jest with TypeScript | TypeScript Jest transformer |\n\n## Tooling\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `eslint` | Linting (configured via `packages/eslint-config`) |\n| `prettier` | Code formatting |\n| `stylelint` | CSS-in-JS style linting |\n| `knip` | Unused export detection |\n| `husky` | Git hooks |\n| `semver` | Version comparison for auto-update |\n",
