            "content": "# Factory platform overview\n\nFactory is an AI software engineering platform built around Droid — an autonomous AI agent that runs in the developer's terminal, performs multi-step coding tasks, and coordinates with a cloud backend for session management, billing, and integrations.\n\nThe monorepo contains every product surface: the Droid CLI, the background daemon that manages agent processes, a web and desktop app for interacting with sessions, a REST API backend, Firebase Cloud Functions, infrastructure-as-code, and a collection of shared libraries.\n\n## What the platform does\n\nA developer installs the `droid` CLI, authenticates, and types a task in natural language. Droid spins up an agent loop, calls LLMs, invokes file-system and shell tools, and streams progress to the user's terminal in a full-screen TUI. Sessions persist in the cloud and can be resumed, paused, or reviewed in the web app.\n\nThe system supports both local machines and remote cloud development environments (CDEs). On desktop, the daemon runs locally inside the Electron app. In a remote workspace it runs as a standalone binary managed by the platform.\n\n## Quick links\n\n| Topic | Where to look |\n|---|---|\n| Getting started | [Getting started](getting-started.md) |\n| Architecture diagram | [Architecture](architecture.md) |\n| Key terms | [Glossary](glossary.md) |\n| Contributing | [How to contribute](../how-to-contribute/index.md) |\n| CLI app deep-dive | [apps/cli](../apps/cli/index.md) |\n| Daemon | [apps/daemon](../apps/daemon.md) |\n| Web app | [apps/web](../apps/web.md) |\n| Design system | [packages/core-ui](../packages/core-ui.md) |\n| AI agent core | [packages/droid-core](../packages/droid-core.md) |\n| Codebase stats | [By the numbers](../by-the-numbers.md) |\n| History | [Lore](../lore.md) |\n\n## Monorepo map\n\n```\nfactory-mono/\n├── apps/\n│   ├── cli/            # Droid CLI (Bun, Ink/React TUI + Commander headless)\n│   ├── daemon/         # factoryd background service (Bun, WebSocket/JSON-RPC)\n│   ├── web/            # Main web app (Vite + React)\n│   ├── desktop/        # Electron desktop wrapper\n│   ├── backend/        # REST API (Next.js 15)\n│   ├── admin/          # Admin dashboard (Next.js 15)\n│   ├── functions/      # Firebase Cloud Functions\n│   ├── signal/         # Real-time notification service\n│   ├── scripts/        # Build and maintenance scripts\n│   └── ...\n├── packages/\n│   ├── core-ui/        # Mandatory design system\n│   ├── frontend/       # Shared React features\n│   ├── droid-core/     # AI agent logic, LLM integrations, tools\n│   ├── common/         # Shared types, enums, API contracts\n│   ├── daemon-core/    # Daemon business logic\n│   ├── services/       # Service layer abstractions\n│   ├── models/         # Data model schemas\n│   ├── logging/        # Logging, metrics, error classes\n│   ├── updater/        # Auto-update utilities\n│   └── ...\n├── infra/              # OpenTofu infrastructure\n└── internal/           # Internal tools and admin web\n```\n\n## Tech stack at a glance\n\n| Layer | Technologies |\n|---|---|\n| CLI / daemon | Bun runtime, TypeScript, Ink (React for terminals) |\n| Web / desktop | Vite, React 19, Redux Toolkit, styled-components, Electron |\n| Backend | Next.js 15, TypeScript |\n| Database | Firebase Firestore |\n| Auth | WorkOS AuthKit |\n| LLMs | OpenAI, Anthropic (Claude), Google Gemini |\n| Observability | Sentry, custom metrics via Datadog / Axiom |\n| Feature flags | Statsig |\n| Billing | Orb |\n| Infra | OpenTofu (Terraform-compatible), AWS, Firebase |\n| Build | Turborepo, npm workspaces |\n",
