            "content": "# Missions\n\nActive contributors: arman, tchourakov, alvinsng\n\n## Purpose\n\nMissions (also known as AGI mode or Colossus/large task decomposition) are a way to break very large engineering tasks into parallel sub-tasks that multiple Droid agents execute simultaneously. Where a regular session has one agent working through steps sequentially, a mission orchestrates a fleet of agents across a shared codebase.\n\n## How missions work\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    A[\"User enters mission\\ndroid enter-mission\"] --> B[\"Mission controller\\ndecomposes task\"]\n    B --> C[\"Worker agent 1\"]\n    B --> D[\"Worker agent 2\"]\n    B --> E[\"Worker agent N\"]\n    C --> F[\"Aggregation / merge\"]\n    D --> F\n    E --> F\n    F --> G[\"Mission output\\nto user\"]\n```\n\nThe orchestrating agent uses the Task tool (`apps/cli/src/task/`) to spawn sub-agents. Each sub-agent is a fresh Droid session that executes a sub-task and reports results back.\n\n## Entry and exit\n\nThe `enter-mission` command (`apps/cli/src/commands/enter-mission.ts`) transitions the CLI into mission mode. The `exit-mission` command returns to normal session mode.\n\nUsers can also navigate between missions with `apps/cli/src/commands/missions.ts` (list) and `apps/cli/src/commands/mission.ts` (view a single mission).\n\n## Task tool\n\nThe Task tool is how the orchestrating agent spawns sub-agents. It is dynamically registered at runtime via `apps/cli/src/task/`. The tool accepts a prompt, a subagent type identifier, and a description. The CLI looks up available sub-agent types from `.factory/droids/` configuration files.\n\n## Integration points\n\n- `apps/cli/src/commands/enter-mission.ts` — mission entry\n- `apps/cli/src/task/` — dynamic Task tool registration\n- `apps/backend` — mission sessions are persisted like regular sessions\n- `packages/frontend/src/features/missions/` — web UI for viewing missions\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/cli/src/commands/enter-mission.ts` | Enter mission mode |\n| `apps/cli/src/commands/exit-mission.ts` | Exit mission mode |\n| `apps/cli/src/commands/missions.ts` | List all missions |\n| `apps/cli/src/task/` | Task tool (sub-agent spawning) |\n",
