            "content": "# Deployment\n\nFactory is deployed across several independent targets. Each component has its own release workflow and delivery mechanism.\n\n## What deploys where\n\n| Component | Target | Workflow |\n|-----------|--------|----------|\n| Web app (`apps/web`) | Vercel | `deploy-dev-web.yml`, `deploy-prod-app.yml` |\n| Backend API (`apps/backend`) | Vercel | `deploy-prod-admin.yml`, `deploy-prod.yml` |\n| Admin dashboard (`apps/admin`) | Vercel | `deploy-prod-admin.yml` |\n| Relay Lambda | AWS (us-west-1) | `deploy-relay-aws.yml` |\n| Firebase Cloud Functions | Firebase | `deploy-prod.yml` |\n| CLI binary (`droid`) | S3 + npm | `cli-release.yml`, `cli-release-npm.yml` |\n| Daemon binary (`factoryd`) | S3 + CDE sandboxes | `factoryd-release.yml` |\n| Desktop app | S3 (auto-update) | `desktop-release.yml` |\n| Infrastructure | AWS via OpenTofu | `opentofu.yml` |\n\n## Sub-pages\n\n- [Releases](./releases.md) — release cadence, version bumping, per-component release process\n- [Environments](./environments.md) — production, development, staging, localhost differences\n- [Infrastructure](./infra.md) — AWS, Firebase, Vercel, OpenTofu configuration\n",
