            "content": "# System architecture\n\nFactory is a monorepo with six deployable applications and seventeen shared packages. The core communication path runs from a user interface (web or desktop) through a daemon process to the Droid CLI, which executes the agent loop.\n\n## High-level component map\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    subgraph \"User interfaces\"\n        WEB[\"apps/web\\n(Vite + React)\"]\n        DESKTOP[\"apps/desktop\\n(Electron)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph \"Backend\"\n        API[\"apps/backend\\n(Next.js 15 API)\"]\n        ADMIN[\"apps/admin\\n(Next.js 15)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph \"Agent runtime\"\n        DAEMON[\"apps/daemon (factoryd)\\nWebSocket JSON-RPC server\"]\n        CLI[\"apps/cli (droid)\\nAgent loop + TUI\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph \"Shared packages\"\n        DROIDCORE[\"@factory/droid-core\\nTools, LLMs, streaming\"]\n        FRONTEND[\"@factory/frontend\\nShared React features\"]\n        COREUI[\"@factory/core-ui\\nDesign system\"]\n        COMMON[\"@factory/common\\nTypes, enums, contracts\"]\n        DAEMONCORE[\"@factory/daemon-core\\nServer, terminal mgmt\"]\n    end\n\n    WEB -->|\"WebSocket JSON-RPC\"| DAEMON\n    DESKTOP -->|\"WebSocket JSON-RPC\"| DAEMON\n    DAEMON -->|\"stdin/stdout JSON-RPC\"| CLI\n    WEB -->|\"HTTP REST\"| API\n    DESKTOP -->|\"HTTP REST\"| API\n\n    CLI --> DROIDCORE\n    DAEMON --> DAEMONCORE\n    WEB --> FRONTEND\n    DESKTOP --> FRONTEND\n    FRONTEND --> COREUI\n    DROIDCORE --> COMMON\n    DAEMONCORE --> COMMON\n```\n\n## Three-tier communication\n\nThe main data path for a droid session has three distinct layers, each with its own transport protocol:\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant Frontend as apps/web or apps/desktop\n    participant Daemon as apps/daemon (factoryd)\n    participant CLI as apps/cli (droid)\n\n    Frontend->>Daemon: WebSocket JSON-RPC 2.0\n    Note over Frontend,Daemon: daemon.initialize_session, daemon.add_user_message, etc.\n\n    Daemon->>CLI: stdin/stdout JSON-RPC 2.0\n    Note over Daemon,CLI: Spawns droid process per session\n\n    CLI->>Daemon: Notifications (session_notification, request_permission)\n    Daemon->>Frontend: Forwarded notifications via WebSocket\n```\n\nThe protocol contracts are defined in `packages/common/src/droid/enums.ts` (method names, notification types) and `packages/common/src/droid/schemas/` (message schemas).\n\n## Agent execution flow\n\nWhen a user sends a message, the following happens inside the CLI:\n\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    MSG[\"User message\"] --> LOOP[\"Agent loop\\n(streamingJsonRpcExecRunner)\"]\n    LOOP --> LLM[\"LLM provider\\n(Anthropic, OpenAI, Google)\"]\n    LLM --> TOOL[\"Tool selection\"]\n    TOOL --> CONFIRM[\"Tool confirmation\\n(ask daemon/frontend)\"]\n    CONFIRM --> EXEC[\"Tool execution\\n(Edit, Execute, Read, etc.)\"]\n    EXEC --> LOOP\n    LOOP --> DONE[\"Response complete\"]\n```\n\nThe main agent loop lives in `apps/cli/src/exec/streamingJsonRpcExecRunner.ts`. Tool definitions come from `packages/droid-core/src/tools/definitions/`. Each tool call may require user confirmation, which the CLI requests through the daemon to the frontend.\n\n## LLM providers\n\nThe CLI and droid-core support three provider families:\n\n| Provider | Package |\n|---|---|\n| Anthropic (Claude) | `packages/droid-core/src/llms/provider/anthropic/` |\n| OpenAI (GPT, o-series) | `packages/droid-core/src/llms/provider/openai/` |\n| Google (Gemini) | `packages/droid-core/src/llms/provider/google/` |\n\nThe backend also acts as an LLM proxy (`apps/backend/src/app/api/llm/`) so all requests can flow through Factory infrastructure for rate limiting, usage tracking, and billing.\n\n## Data persistence\n\nSessions and messages are stored in Firestore. The backend service layer at `apps/backend/src/services/` handles all persistence. The CLI and daemon are stateless beyond in-memory session data; long-term storage happens via backend API calls.\n\n## Deployment topology\n\n| Runtime | Where it runs |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/backend` | Vercel (Next.js) |\n| `apps/web` | Vercel (Vite SPA) |\n| `apps/admin` | Vercel |\n| `apps/daemon` | Bundled in desktop app (local), or downloaded to CDEs (remote) |\n| `apps/cli` | Installed locally via npm or SEA binary, or run on CDEs |\n| `apps/desktop` | Distributed as Electron app with auto-update |\n\nFor more detail on individual components, see:\n- [Apps overview](../apps/index.md)\n- [Packages overview](../packages/index.md)\n- [Daemon: session management](../apps/daemon/session-management.md)\n- [Droid-core: tool system](../packages/droid-core/tools.md)\n",
            "file_path": "/Users/jonathanlucuix-andre/Documents/test-repos/factory-mono/droid-wiki/overview/architecture.md"
          },
