            "content": "# @factory/core-ui\n\n`packages/core-ui` is the Factory design system. All web UI across `apps/web`, `apps/desktop`, `apps/admin`, and `packages/frontend` must use its components. Using raw HTML elements (`<div>`, `<button>`, `<input>`) directly is prohibited and enforced by ESLint.\n\n## Purpose\n\n`@factory/core-ui` provides layout primitives, form components, typography elements, and a semantic color token system. It handles light/dark mode switching and ensures visual consistency across all Factory interfaces.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/core-ui/src/\n├── colors/         # Semantic color system and tokens\n├── fonts/          # Font loading and configuration\n├── form/           # Form field wrappers\n├── hooks/          # Utility hooks (useScrollIntoView, etc.)\n├── icons/          # Icon wrappers\n├── primitives/     # Core layout and UI components (32 components)\n├── styles/         # Global styles and CSS reset\n├── tokens/         # Design tokens (spacing, radii, shadows)\n├── typography/     # Text and heading components\n└── utils/          # Styling utilities\n```\n\n## Key primitives\n\n| Component | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `Box` | Base layout container (replaces `<div>`) |\n| `Flex` | Flexbox layout container |\n| `Grid` | CSS Grid container |\n| `Button` | Interactive button with variants |\n| `Input` | Text input |\n| `Dropdown` | Select/dropdown component |\n| `Text` | Inline text with typography variants |\n| `Header` | Section and page headings |\n| `Collapsible` | Expandable/collapsible section |\n| `Toast` | Notification toast |\n| `Tooltip` | Hover tooltip |\n| `Avatar` | User/org avatar display |\n| `Badge` | Small status indicator badge |\n| `Separator` | Visual divider |\n\n## Color system\n\nColors use semantic naming rather than raw hex values. The token system maps semantic names to actual colors in both light and dark modes:\n\n```typescript\nimport { colors } from '@factory/core-ui';\n\n// Use semantic tokens\nconst buttonBackground = colors.semantics.actionPrimary;\nconst textMuted = colors.semantics.textSecondary;\n```\n\nThe color definitions are in `packages/core-ui/src/colors/`. Never use hardcoded hex values in component code.\n\n## Design tokens\n\nSpacing, border radius, shadow, and other values come from the token system in `packages/core-ui/src/tokens/`:\n\n```typescript\nimport { tokens } from '@factory/core-ui';\n\nconst spacing = tokens.spacing.md;   // 8px\nconst radius = tokens.radius.sm;     // 4px\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nAll components are exported from the package root:\n\n```typescript\nimport { Box, Flex, Button, Text } from '@factory/core-ui';\n```\n\nSee the Storybook for interactive documentation of all components: `npm run storybook` from the repo root.\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `packages/core-ui/src/index.ts` | Package exports |\n| `packages/core-ui/src/primitives/` | 32 component implementations |\n| `packages/core-ui/src/colors/` | Semantic color token definitions |\n| `packages/core-ui/src/tokens/` | Design token values |\n\n## See also\n\n- [Primitives reference](primitives.md)\n- [UI development guide](../../how-to-contribute/patterns-and-conventions.md)\n",
