            "content": "# Core-UI primitives\n\nThe `packages/core-ui/src/primitives/` directory contains 32 UI component implementations. Each maps to a standard HTML/CSS pattern but enforces design system constraints.\n\n## Layout primitives\n\n### Box\n\nThe fundamental building block. Use instead of `<div>`:\n\n```typescript\n<Box padding=\"md\" backgroundColor=\"semantics.surfacePrimary\">\n  content\n</Box>\n```\n\nAccepts standard CSS properties as props, mapped to design tokens where applicable.\n\n### Flex\n\nA `Box` with `display: flex` and flexbox-specific props:\n\n```typescript\n<Flex direction=\"row\" gap=\"sm\" align=\"center\" justify=\"space-between\">\n  <Text>Left</Text>\n  <Button>Action</Button>\n</Flex>\n```\n\n### Grid\n\nA `Box` with `display: grid`:\n\n```typescript\n<Grid columns={3} gap=\"md\">\n  {items.map(item => <Card key={item.id} {...item} />)}\n</Grid>\n```\n\n## Typography\n\n### Text\n\nInline and block text with variants:\n\n```typescript\n<Text variant=\"body\" color=\"semantics.textPrimary\">Content</Text>\n<Text variant=\"caption\" color=\"semantics.textSecondary\">Metadata</Text>\n```\n\nVariants: `body`, `caption`, `label`, `code`, `mono`.\n\n### Header\n\nSection and page headings:\n\n```typescript\n<Header level={1}>Page title</Header>\n<Header level={2}>Section title</Header>\n<Header level={3}>Subsection</Header>\n```\n\n## Interactive components\n\n### Button\n\n```typescript\n<Button variant=\"primary\" onClick={handler}>Submit</Button>\n<Button variant=\"secondary\" disabled>Cancel</Button>\n<Button variant=\"ghost\" size=\"sm\">More</Button>\n```\n\nVariants: `primary`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `danger`.\nSizes: `xs`, `sm`, `md` (default), `lg`.\n\n### Input\n\n```typescript\n<Input\n  value={value}\n  onChange={setValue}\n  placeholder=\"Enter text...\"\n  error={errorMessage}\n/>\n```\n\n### Dropdown\n\n```typescript\n<Dropdown\n  options={[{ value: 'a', label: 'Option A' }]}\n  value={selected}\n  onChange={setSelected}\n/>\n```\n\n## Feedback components\n\n### Toast\n\nNotifications rendered via the `ToastProvider`. Trigger with the `useToast` hook:\n\n```typescript\nconst { showToast } = useToast();\nshowToast({ message: 'Saved!', variant: 'success' });\n```\n\nVariants: `success`, `error`, `warning`, `info`.\n\n### Collapsible\n\n```typescript\n<Collapsible header={<Text>Show more</Text>} defaultOpen={false}>\n  <Box>Expanded content</Box>\n</Collapsible>\n```\n\n## Utility components\n\n### Avatar\n\n```typescript\n<Avatar src={user.avatarUrl} name={user.displayName} size=\"md\" />\n```\n\nFalls back to initials if no image is provided.\n\n### Badge\n\n```typescript\n<Badge variant=\"success\">Active</Badge>\n<Badge variant=\"warning\">Pending</Badge>\n```\n\nVariants: `default`, `success`, `warning`, `error`, `info`.\n\n### Separator\n\n```typescript\n<Separator orientation=\"horizontal\" />\n<Separator orientation=\"vertical\" />\n```\n\n### Tooltip\n\n```typescript\n<Tooltip content=\"This action cannot be undone\">\n  <Button variant=\"danger\">Delete</Button>\n</Tooltip>\n```\n\n## Accessing all components\n\nAll primitives are exported from `packages/core-ui/src/index.ts`. Import directly:\n\n```typescript\nimport { Box, Flex, Button, Text, Input, Toast } from '@factory/core-ui';\n```\n",
