            "content": "# Factory monorepo\n\nFactory is an AI-powered software engineering platform. The monorepo contains the entire product: a web dashboard, an Electron desktop app, the Droid CLI (the primary AI coding agent), a background daemon that manages agent processes, a backend API, and a shared library layer that ties them together.\n\nUsers interact with Factory through the Droid CLI in their terminal or through the web/desktop interfaces. The CLI runs an AI agent that can read code, edit files, run commands, search the web, and interact with external tools via MCP. Sessions are managed by the daemon (`factoryd`), which bridges the CLI and the frontend over WebSocket JSON-RPC.\n\n## What lives here\n\n| Directory | What it contains |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/` | Deployable applications: backend, web, desktop, CLI, daemon, signal, relay, and more |\n| `packages/` | Shared libraries consumed by apps: `core-ui`, `frontend`, `droid-core`, `common`, `services`, etc. |\n| `infra/` | OpenTofu (Terraform) infrastructure-as-code, Ansible playbooks, Lambda functions |\n| `internal/` | Internal-only tooling and admin apps |\n| `docs/` | Engineering guides and conventions |\n\n## Quick orientation\n\n- **Want to understand the architecture?** Read [Architecture](./architecture.md).\n- **Want to set up a dev environment?** Read [Getting started](./getting-started.md).\n- **Want to change the CLI or daemon?** Start with [CLI](../apps/cli/index.md) or [Daemon](../apps/daemon.md), then read [Debugging](../how-to-contribute/debugging.md).\n- **Want to build frontend features?** Read the [Frontend package](../packages/frontend/index.md) and [core-ui](../packages/core-ui.md) pages.\n- **Looking for API types?** Check [common package](../packages/common.md).\n\n## Technology stack\n\n| Layer | Tech |\n|---|---|\n| Monorepo tooling | npm workspaces, Turborepo |\n| Backend API | Next.js 15, Vercel |\n| Web app | Vite, React 19 |\n| Desktop | Electron, Vite, React 19 |\n| CLI | Bun, TypeScript, Commander.js, Ink (React for terminals) |\n| Daemon | Bun, WebSocket, JSON-RPC 2.0 |\n| Design system | `@factory/core-ui` (styled-components, semantic color tokens) |\n| State management | Redux Toolkit (frontend), Jotai atoms (CLI) |\n| Auth | WorkOS AuthKit |\n| Feature flags | Statsig |\n| Error tracking | Sentry |\n| Metrics/logging | Axiom, custom `@factory/logging` package |\n| Infrastructure | OpenTofu, AWS, Google Cloud, Vercel |\n| Testing | Jest, Vitest, Playwright (e2e), `@microsoft/tui-test` (CLI e2e) |\n",
