            "content": "# Debugging\n\n## Architecture recap\n\n```\nFrontend (DaemonSessionController.ts)\n    ↓ WebSocket JSON-RPC\nDaemon (droid-request-handler.ts)\n    ↓ stdin/stdout JSON-RPC\nCLI (streamingJsonRpcExecRunner.tsx)\n```\n\nMessages flow through three layers. Debugging usually means figuring out which layer dropped or mangled a message.\n\n## Log file locations\n\n| Environment | Directory | Key files |\n|---|---|---|\n| Production | `~/.factory/logs/` | `factoryd.log`, `droid-log-single.log`, `console.log` |\n| Development | `~/.factory-dev/logs/` | Same files, dev builds |\n\nDev environment uses `~/.factory-dev/`, not `~/.factory/`.\n\nDev server logs also go to:\n\n- `/tmp/factory-dev-backend.log`\n- `/tmp/factory-dev-admin.log`\n- `/tmp/factory-dev-desktop.log`\n- `/tmp/factory-dev-daemon.log`\n\n## Tracing a message\n\n```bash\n# Check CLI emitted the message\ngrep \"your-feature\" ~/.factory-dev/logs/droid-log-single.log\n\n# Check daemon received/forwarded it\ngrep \"your-feature\" ~/.factory-dev/logs/factoryd.log\n\n# Watch all logs in real-time\ntail -f ~/.factory-dev/logs/*.log\n```\n\n## Common issues\n\n### Changes not appearing\n\n1. Rebuild CLI: `cd apps/cli && npm run setup`\n2. Restart the daemon process\n3. Start a new session (old sessions do not pick up changes)\n4. Check you are looking at the right log directory (`~/.factory-dev/` for dev)\n\n### Timing issues\n\nNotifications sent before a session is registered with the daemon are lost. Always emit notifications after session initialization completes.\n\n### Schema mismatches\n\nIf the CLI sends a notification but the frontend does not receive it:\n\n1. Check the notification type is in the `SessionNotificationType` enum (`packages/common/src/droid/enums.ts`)\n2. Check the schema is defined in `packages/common/src/droid/schemas/cli.ts`\n3. Check a frontend handler exists in `DaemonSessionController.ts`\n\n## Adding debug logging\n\n```ts\nimport { logInfo } from '@factory/logging';\n\nlogInfo('[Feature] Event received', { count: items.length });\n```\n\n## Quick debug checklist\n\n- Rebuilt CLI after changes (`npm run setup`)\n- Restarted daemon process\n- Started new session (not reusing old one)\n- Checking correct log directory (`~/.factory-dev/` for dev)\n- Schema/enum changes are in `@factory/common`\n- Frontend handler exists for the notification type\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `packages/common/src/droid/enums.ts` | Notification type enums |\n| `packages/common/src/droid/schemas/` | JSON-RPC message schemas |\n| `apps/cli/src/exec/streamingJsonRpcExecRunner.tsx` | CLI-side JSON-RPC handling |\n| `apps/daemon/src/server/handlers/droid-request-handler.ts` | Daemon request routing |\n| `packages/frontend/src/services/session/DaemonSessionController.ts` | Frontend session controller |\n",
