            "content": "# CLI command structure\n\nThe CLI uses Commander.js for command parsing. Commands are defined in `apps/cli/src/commands/` with each file exporting a function that registers its command with the Commander program.\n\n## Command categories\n\n### Session and agent\n\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `exec` | `exec.ts` | Run the AI agent loop (the core interactive command) |\n| `sessions` | `sessions.ts` | List, search, and manage sessions |\n| `new` | `new.ts` | Start a new session |\n| `fork` | `fork.ts` | Fork an existing session |\n| `rename` | `rename.ts` | Rename a session |\n| `share` | `share.ts` | Share a session URL |\n| `copy` | `copy.ts` | Copy session content |\n| `rewind` | `rewind.ts` | Rewind to an earlier point in a session |\n| `search` | `search.ts` | Search session history |\n| `favorite` | `favorite.ts` | Toggle session favorites |\n| `compact` | `compact.ts` | Compact session context |\n\n### Authentication and account\n\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `login` | `loginCommand.ts` | Authenticate with Factory |\n| `logout` | `logoutCommand.ts` | Clear auth credentials |\n| `account` | `account.ts` | View account info |\n| `billing` | `billing.ts` | Billing and usage information |\n\n### Agent configuration\n\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `model` | `model.ts` | Select and configure LLM model |\n| `language` | `language.ts` | Set interface language |\n| `settings` | `settings.ts` | CLI configuration |\n| `settings-debug` | `settings-debug.ts` | Debug settings |\n\n### Tools and extensions\n\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `mcp/` | `mcp/` | MCP server management (install, list, configure) |\n| `plugins` | `plugins.ts` | Plugin management |\n| `skills` | `skills.ts` | Skill management |\n| `create-skill` | `create-skill.ts` | Create a new skill |\n| `hooks` | `hooks.ts` | Git hook management |\n| `droids` | `droids.ts` | Custom droid management |\n\n### Missions (multi-agent)\n\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `mission` | `mission.ts` | View mission status |\n| `missions` | `missions.ts` | List missions |\n| `enter-mission` | `enter-mission.ts` | Enter mission mode |\n| `exit-mission` | `exit-mission.ts` | Exit mission mode |\n\n### Infrastructure\n\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `ssh` | `ssh.ts` | SSH into remote CDEs |\n| `computer` | `computer.ts` | Manage BYOI computers |\n| `daemon` | `daemon.ts` | Daemon management |\n| `ide` | `ide.ts` | IDE integration commands |\n| `update` | `update.ts` | Self-update CLI binary |\n\n### Utilities\n\n| Command | File | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `bug` | `bug.ts` | File bug reports |\n| `wiki-upload` | `wiki-upload.ts` | Upload wiki documentation |\n| `status` | `status.ts` | Show CLI status |\n| `diagnostics` | `diagnostics.ts` | Run diagnostic checks |\n| `help` | `help.ts` | Show help information |\n| `review` | `review.ts` | PR review |\n| `cost` | `cost.ts` | Show session cost |\n| `limits` | `limits.ts` | Show usage limits |\n| `git-ai` | `git-ai.ts` | AI-assisted git operations |\n| `generate-blog` | `generate-blog.ts` | Generate blog content from sessions |\n\n## Command registration\n\nCommands are registered through `src/commands/index.ts`, which imports and wires up each command with the Commander program. The `assertValidOptions.ts` module validates command options before execution.\n",
