            "content": "# CLI TUI rendering\n\nThe Droid CLI's interactive mode is a full-screen terminal application built with React and Ink. This page covers the rendering architecture.\n\n## Technology\n\n- **Ink** (v6.7.0) -- React renderer for the terminal. Components return Ink primitives (`<Box>`, `<Text>`) instead of HTML elements.\n- **React 19** -- standard hooks, context, and component patterns\n- **Jotai** -- atom-based state management for CLI state\n\n## Component hierarchy\n\nThe TUI root is `src/app.tsx`, which is the largest file in the repo at around 160KB. It manages:\n\n- Session initialization and lifecycle\n- Agent message rendering\n- Tool call display and approval\n- Input handling\n- Status bar and notifications\n\nKey component directories:\n\n| Directory | Contents |\n|---|---|\n| `src/components/` | ~120 Ink React components |\n| `src/hooks/` | ~70 custom hooks for state, effects, and interactions |\n| `src/contexts/` | React context providers for session, agent, and UI state |\n\n## State management\n\nThe CLI uses a mix of:\n\n- **Jotai atoms** -- for global state (session, messages, settings)\n- **React useState/useReducer** -- for component-local state\n- **React context** -- for dependency injection (agent services, session controller)\n\n## Rendering flow\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    App[app.tsx] --> SessionProvider[Session Context]\n    SessionProvider --> AgentView[Agent Message View]\n    SessionProvider --> InputArea[User Input Area]\n    SessionProvider --> StatusBar[Status Bar]\n    AgentView --> MessageList[Message List]\n    MessageList --> ToolCallDisplay[Tool Call Display]\n    MessageList --> MarkdownRenderer[Markdown Renderer]\n    InputArea --> TextInput[Text Input Component]\n```\n\n## E2E testing\n\nTUI E2E tests use `@microsoft/tui-test`, which captures terminal snapshots and simulates keyboard input. Tests are in `apps/cli/e2e-tests/` and configured via `tui-test.config.ts`.\n\n```bash\n# Run TUI E2E tests\ncd apps/cli && npx tui-test\n```\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/app.tsx` | TUI root component |\n| `src/main.tsx` | TUI initialization (Ink render setup) |\n| `src/components/` | All Ink React components |\n| `src/hooks/` | Custom React hooks |\n| `src/contexts/` | Context providers |\n| `e2e-tests/` | TUI E2E test suites |\n| `tui-test.config.ts` | E2E test configuration |\n",
