e.ts`) handles:\n\n- Authentication token validation\n- Route-level authorization\n- Request logging and breadcrumbs\n- Error formatting via `handleRouteMiddleware`\n\nAPI types for request/response shapes live in `packages/common/src/api/{service}/types.ts`.\n\n## Development\n\nStarted as part of `npm run dev:web`. Logs go to `/tmp/factory-dev-backend.log`. Port 3000.\n\n```bash\n# Run backend tests\nnpm run test -- --filter=apps/backend\ncd apps/backend && npx jest path/to/file.test.ts\n```\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/middleware.ts` | Request middleware (auth, logging, error handling) |\n| `src/app/api/` | All REST API route handlers |\n| `src/services/` | Business logic services |\n| `jest.config.ts` | Test configuration |\n| `vercel.json` | Vercel deployment config |\n",
