            "content": "# core-ui\n\n`@factory/core-ui` (`packages/core-ui`) is the mandatory design system for all Factory UI development. Every frontend component must use core-ui primitives instead of raw HTML elements.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/core-ui/src/\n├── colors/           # Semantic color system (light/dark mode)\n├── fonts/            # Font family definitions\n├── form/             # Form components\n├── hooks/            # UI hooks\n├── icons/            # Icon components\n├── primitives/       # Layout and UI primitives (~30 components)\n├── styles/           # Global styles and theme\n├── tokens/           # Design tokens\n├── typography/       # Typography components\n├── utils/            # UI utilities\n└── index.ts          # Package entry point (exports everything)\n```\n\n## Component categories\n\n### Layout primitives\n\n| Component | Replaces | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Box` | `<div>` | Base layout primitive with style props |\n| `Flex` | `<div style=\"display:flex\">` | Flexbox layout |\n| `Grid` | `<div style=\"display:grid\">` | CSS Grid layout |\n\n### Form components\n\n| Component | Replaces | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Button` | `<button>` | Button with variants and states |\n| `Input` | `<input>` | Text input with validation |\n| `Dropdown` | `<select>` | Dropdown menu |\n\n### Typography\n\n| Component | Replaces | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Header` | `<h1>`-`<h6>` | Heading component |\n| `Text` | `<p>`, `<span>` | Text with semantic variants |\n\n### Interactive\n\n| Component | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `Collapsible` | Expandable/collapsible content |\n| `Toast` | Toast notifications (with `ToastProvider`) |\n\n## Color system\n\nColors use semantic tokens defined in `src/colors/`. Never hardcode hex values.\n\n```ts\nimport { colors } from '@factory/core-ui';\n\n// Use semantic tokens\ncolors.semantics.primary\ncolors.semantics.text\ncolors.semantics.surface\ncolors.semantics.border\n```\n\nThe color system supports light and dark modes automatically.\n\n## Icons\n\nAn extensive icon set is available at `@factory/core-ui/icons`. Icons are individual components.\n\n## Rules\n\n- Always use `Box`/`Flex`/`Grid` for layout, never raw `<div>`\n- Always use `Button`/`Input`/`Dropdown` for forms, never raw HTML\n- Always use `Header`/`Text` for typography\n- Always use `colors.semantics` for colors, never hardcode\n- Use `FontFamilies` constants for fonts\n- Do not use inline styles for simple styling; prefer component props\n\n## Storybook\n\nBrowse all components and their usage in Storybook. The \"Design System/Colors\" story shows all available color tokens.\n\n```bash\nnpm run storybook\n```\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/index.ts` | Package entry point and all exports |\n| `src/primitives/` | Layout and UI primitives |\n| `src/colors/` | Semantic color system |\n| `src/icons/` | Icon components |\n| `src/typography/` | Typography components |\n",
