            "content": "# Deployment\n\nFactory components deploy through different pipelines depending on their runtime.\n\n## Deployment targets\n\n| Component | Platform | Trigger | Workflow |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Backend | Vercel | Merge to `main` | `deploy-prod.yml` |\n| Web | Vercel | Merge to `main` | `deploy-prod.yml` |\n| Admin | Vercel | Merge to `main` | `deploy-prod-admin.yml` |\n| CLI | Binary release (S3/npm) | Release tag | `cli-release.yml`, `cli-release-npm.yml` |\n| Desktop | Electron Forge (S3) | Release tag | `desktop-release.yml` |\n| Daemon | Binary release (S3) | Release tag | `factoryd-release.yml` |\n| Signal | GCP Cloud Functions | Deploy script | `signal-deploy.yml` |\n| Relay | AWS | Deploy script | `deploy-relay-aws.yml` |\n| VS Code extension | VS Marketplace | Release tag | `vscode-extension-release.yml` |\n| JetBrains plugin | JetBrains Marketplace | Release tag | `jetbrains-plugin-release.yml` |\n\n## Release process\n\n1. **Daily releases** are cut from `dev` to `main` via `release-cut.yml`\n2. **Hotfix releases** use `hotfix-cut.yml` for urgent patches to `main`\n3. **Post-release validation** runs via `post-release-validation.yml` after each release\n4. **Version bumping** is automated via `release-bump-version.yml`\n\n## Infrastructure\n\nThe `infra/` directory contains:\n\n| Component | Path | Technology |\n|---|---|---|\n| AWS resources | `infra/common/` | OpenTofu (Terraform) |\n| Lambda functions | `infra/lambda_code/` | Python |\n| Lambda layers | `infra/lambda_layers/` | Python dependencies |\n| Ansible playbooks | `infra/ansible/` | VM provisioning |\n| Terraform imports | `infra/terraform_imports/` | State migration helpers |\n| Mise tasks | `infra/mise-tasks/` | Automation scripts |\n\nInfrastructure changes use OpenTofu (not Terraform) for validation:\n\n```bash\ncd infra && tofu init && tofu validate && tofu fmt\n```\n\n## Environment configuration\n\nBackend environment variables are managed through `.env` files per environment:\n- `.env.production`\n- `.env.development`\n- `.env.localhost`\n- `.env.staging`\n\nSee `apps/backend/.env.example` for the required variables.\n\n## Dev deployment\n\nDev web deployment is triggered by `deploy-dev-web.yml` for testing changes before release.\n",
