            "content": "# Data models\n\nKey data structures and where they are defined.\n\n## Core domain models\n\n| Model | Package | Path | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Session | `@factory/common` | `src/session/` | Session metadata, state, and configuration |\n| Message | `@factory/common` | `src/session/` | Chat messages (user, assistant, tool results) |\n| Organization | `@factory/common` | `src/organization/` | Multi-tenant organization |\n| User | `@factory/common` | `src/api/` | User profile and auth |\n| Tool call | `@factory/common` | `src/tools/` | Tool invocation and result |\n| Integration | `@factory/common` | `src/integrations/` | Third-party service connections |\n\n## Protocol models\n\n| Model | Package | Path | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| JSON-RPC request | `@factory/common` | `src/droid/schemas/` | Daemon-CLI protocol requests |\n| JSON-RPC notification | `@factory/common` | `src/droid/enums.ts` | Notification type enum |\n| Session notification | `@factory/common` | `src/droid/schemas/cli.ts` | CLI-to-daemon notifications |\n\n## LLM models\n\n| Model | Package | Path | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| LLM message | `@factory/droid-core` | `src/messages/` | Messages sent to/from LLM providers |\n| Tool definition | `@factory/droid-core` | `src/tools/` | JSON schema for tool parameters |\n| LLM adapter | `@factory/droid-core` | `src/llms/` | Provider-specific interfaces |\n\n## Data model package\n\n`@factory/models` (`packages/models`) contains additional TypeScript data model schemas used across the codebase.\n\n## API types\n\nAPI request/response types follow a strict convention and live in `packages/common/src/api/{service}/types.ts`. Each backend endpoint has matching types that the frontend imports for type safety.\n",
