            "content": "# Dependencies\n\nKey external dependencies across the monorepo, grouped by purpose. Versions are from `package.json` files as of March 2026.\n\n## AI / LLM\n\n| Package | Version | Used in |\n|---|---|---|\n| `openai` | ^6.25.0 | backend, CLI (via droid-core) |\n| `@anthropic-ai/sdk` | ^0.70.0 | CLI (direct), backend (via proxy) |\n| `@google/genai` | 1.31.0 | backend (Gemini and Vertex AI) |\n\nLLM calls from the CLI go through the daemon, which forwards them to the backend proxy. The proxy handles authentication and routing to the right provider.\n\n## Auth\n\n| Package | Version | Used in |\n|---|---|---|\n| `@workos-inc/node` | ^7.79.3 | backend (server-side token validation) |\n| `@workos-inc/authkit-react` | (frontend dep) | web app (auth UI) |\n\nWorkOS handles user authentication (SSO, magic links, OAuth). The CLI stores the resulting access token in the OS keyring via `keytar`.\n\n## Runtime and CLI frameworks\n\n| Package | Version | Used in |\n|---|---|---|\n| `bun` | 1.3.10 | CLI, daemon (runtime) |\n| `ink` | 6.7.0 | CLI (terminal UI rendering) |\n| `commander` | ^11.0.0 | CLI (command parsing) |\n| `react` | 19.0.2 | CLI (via ink), web app |\n\n## Database and storage\n\n| Package | Version | Used in |\n|---|---|---|\n| `firebase-admin` | (backend dep) | backend, daemon (Firestore access) |\n| `firebase` | (frontend dep) | web app (client-side Firestore) |\n| `firebase-tools` | ^14.4.0 | root (deployment and emulators) |\n\nFirestore is the primary database. There is no SQL layer.\n\n## Monitoring and error reporting\n\n| Package | Version | Used in |\n|---|---|---|\n| `@sentry/nextjs` | ^10.27.0 | backend, web app |\n| `@sentry/node` | ^10.27.0 | daemon |\n| `@opentelemetry/api` | ^1.9.0 | CLI, daemon (tracing) |\n| `@opentelemetry/sdk-metrics` | ^2.2.0 | CLI, daemon |\n\n## Feature flags\n\n| Package | Version | Used in |\n|---|---|---|\n| `@statsig/statsig-node-core` | ^0.6.1 | backend |\n\nFlag names are defined in `package