            "content": "# Packages\n\nFactory's shared code lives in `packages/`. These are npm workspace packages that apps import via `@factory/<name>` paths.\n\n## Core packages\n\n| Package | Description |\n|---|---|\n| [`@factory/core-ui`](./core-ui.md) | Design system — mandatory for all UI development |\n| [`@factory/frontend`](./frontend.md) | Shared React features, hooks, routing, and session management |\n| [`@factory/droid-core`](./droid-core.md) | AI agent core: tool definitions, LLM integrations, streaming |\n| [`@factory/common`](./common.md) | Shared types, enums, API contracts, and feature flag definitions |\n\n## Supporting packages\n\n| Package | Description |\n|---|---|\n| [`@factory/services`](./services.md) | Business logic services shared across apps |\n| `@factory/models` | Data model types and schemas |\n| `@factory/logging` | Centralized logging and error classes |\n| `@factory/utils` | Shared utility functions |\n| `@factory/environment` | Typed environment variable access |\n| `@factory/updater` | Auto-update utilities for CLI/daemon |\n| `@factory/runtime` | Auth storage and runtime utilities |\n| `@factory/daemon-core` | WebSocket server and daemon core logic |\n| `@factory/daemon-client` | Client for communicating with the daemon |\n| `@factory/signal-core` | Signal service core |\n| `@factory/eslint-config` | Shared ESLint configuration and custom rules |\n| `@factory/test-utils` | Shared test helpers and factories |\n\n## Package dependency flow\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    Apps[\"apps/cli, apps/web, apps/desktop\"] --> frontend[\"@factory/frontend\"]\n    Apps --> droid_core[\"@factory/droid-core\"]\n    Apps --> common[\"@factory/common\"]\n    frontend --> core_ui[\"@factory/core-ui\"]\n    frontend --> common\n    droid_core --> common\n    Apps --> services[\"@factory/services\"]\n    services --> common\n    Apps --> logging[\"@factory/logging\"]\n    services --> logging\n```\n\n## Adding a new package\n\n1. Create a directory under `packages/<name>/`\n2. Add a `package.json` with `\"name\": \"@factory/<name>\"`\n3. The workspace is automatically registered (root `package.json` includes `packages/*`)\n4. New shared types go in `@factory/common/src/api/<service>/types.ts`\n",
