            "content": "# @factory/droid-core\n\nActive contributors: jonathanlucuix-andre, factory-droid[bot]\n\n## Purpose\n\n`@factory/droid-core` contains the AI agent's core logic: tool definitions, LLM provider integrations, message handling, and streaming utilities. The CLI and daemon both import from this package to drive the agent loop.\n\n## Directory layout\n\n```\npackages/droid-core/src/\n├── tools/\n│   ├── definitions/          # Tool implementations\n│   │   ├── cli/              # 21 CLI-specific tools (exec, read, write, etc.)\n│   │   ├── file-tools/       # File read/write/edit tools\n│   │   ├── mission/          # Mission orchestration tools\n│   │   ├── todo/             # Todo list tools\n│   │   ├── web/              # Web fetch tools\n│   │   ├── slack/            # Slack integration tools\n│   │   ├── shell.ts          # Shell execution tool\n│   │   ├── globSearch.ts     # Glob file search\n│   │   ├── grepSearch.ts     # Ripgrep search\n│   │   └── schema.ts         # Tool input/output schemas\n│   ├── registry.ts           # Tool registry\n│   ├── types.ts              # Tool type definitions\n│   └── create-tool.ts        # Tool factory function\n├── llms/\n│   ├── providers/            # Anthropic, OpenAI, Google provider wrappers\n│   └── ...                   # LLM utilities and abstractions\n├── streaming/                # Streaming response handlers\n├── messages/                 # Message types and utilities\n├── prompts/                  # System prompt builders\n├── api/                      # API client utilities\n├── automations/              # Automation definitions\n├── droids/                   # Droid configuration types\n├── feature-flags/            # Feature flag integration\n└── core/                     # Core agent loop utilities\n```\n\n## Key abstractions\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/tools/registry.ts` | Tool registry — maps tool names to definitions |\n| `src/tools/types.ts` | `Tool`, `ToolCall`, `ToolResult` type definitions |\n| `src/tools/create-tool.ts` | Factory function for creating typed tool definitions |\n| `src/tools/definitions/schema.ts` | Zod schemas for all tool inputs/outputs |\n| `src/tools/definitions/cli/` | 21 CLI-specific tool implementations |\n| `src/tools/definitions/file-tools/` | File read, write, edit, and multi-edit tools |\n| `src/llms/` | Provider-specific LLM client wrappers (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google) |\n| `src/streaming/` | Streaming token and event handling |\n| `src/messages/` | Message format conversions and utilities |\n| `src/prompts/` | System prompt construction |\n\n## Tool categories\n\n| Category | Examples |\n|---|---|\n| File system | Read, Write, Edit, MultiEdit, Create, LS |\n| Search | Glob, Grep |\n| Shell | Execute (with sandboxing) |\n| Web | FetchUrl, WebSearch |\n| Communication | Slack messages |\n| Agent/orchestration | Task (sub-agents), Mission tools, TodoWrite |\n| Utility | AskUser, ExitSpecMode |\n\n## How tools work\n\nEach tool is created with `create-tool.ts` and has:\n- A name (e.g., `\"Read\"`, `\"Execute\"`)\n- A Zod schema for input validation\n- A handler function that performs the operation and returns a result\n\nThe tool registry maps names to definitions. When the LLM returns a tool call in its response, the agent runner looks up the tool by name, validates the input schema, and calls the handler.\n\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    LLM[\"LLM response\\n(tool_call)\"] --> Runner[\"Agent runner\\n(CLI/exec)\"]\n    Runner --> Registry[\"Tool registry\\nlookup by name\"]\n    Registry --> Tool[\"Tool handler\\n(read file, run shell, etc.)\"]\n    Tool --> Result[\"Tool result\"]\n    Result --> Runner\n    Runner -->|\"next message\"| LLM\n```\n\n## Integration points\n\n- **CLI (`apps/cli`)** — imports tool definitions and registers them per session\n- **LLM providers** — called through the `src/llms/` layer\n- **`@factory/common`** — imports shared types and API contracts\n\n## Key source files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/tools/registry.ts` | Tool registry |\n| `src/tools/types.ts` | Tool type definitions |\n| `src/tools/definitions/schema.ts` | Tool input/output schemas |\n| `src/tools/definitions/file-tools/` | File system tools |\n| `src/llms/` | LLM provider integrations |\n| `src/streaming/` | Streaming utilities |\n\n## Related pages\n\n- [CLI](../apps/cli/index.md) — uses droid-core to run the agent loop\n- [common package](./common.md) — shared types imported by droid-core\n",
